This file contains modifications from the original source code.

Original Project: aeye-lab/python-wmc-battery
Source URL: https://github.com/aeye-lab/python-wmc-battery
Original License: MIT (see LICENSE file)

Modifications made to the original code:

1. Configuration System
   - Replaced PsychoPy's GUI-based configuration with YAML file-based config
   - Config loaded from config.yaml and experiment.yaml instead of runtime dialogs
   - Changed abort key from 'f12' to 'escape' in config/common.yaml

2. Data Output
   - Modified output path structure to: {participant_id}_{language}_{country_code}_{lab_number}_PT{session_id}/
   - Changed data file naming convention
   - Output folder: data/{results_folder}/WMC/

3. Custom Scoring
   - Added spatial_short_term_memory_scorer.py with custom scoring logic
   - Modified scorer to use 'participant_id' instead of 'Subject ID'

4. Eye-Tracking Support
   - Added eye-tracking placeholders (ioDevice, ioConfig, ioSession, ioServer, eyetracker)

5. Dependencies
   - Removed some PsychoPy imports (sound, locale_setup, certain constants)
   - Removed scipy.sparse imports from scorer

6. Code Formatting
   - Various whitespace and formatting changes
   - Code style adjustments

